  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Congestive Heart failure (CHF) is asociated with changes in cardiac function and vascular
      responses. The aim of this study is to characterize these differences. Our hypothesis is,
      that there are differences in vascular responses between healthy subjects and patients with
      CHF.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
